    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "大太监",
        "柴荣",
        "赵匡胤",
        "郭威"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监、大太监引郭威同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凤阁龙楼，万古千秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金殿当头紫阁重，仙人掌上玉芙蓉。太平天子朝元日，五色云车驾六龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤家，郭威。执掌后周天下。昨晚三更时分，偶得一兆，见一红脸大汉，将孤\n左眼伤了一箭，不知主何吉兆？这且不言。柴荣有两个结拜义弟，一个名叫赵\n匡胤，一个名叫郑子明。相约匡胤入朝扶保孤王，这般时候，未见到来。\n来，闪放银安！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪放银安哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（柴荣上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "柴荣",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忙将匡胤事，奏与舅王知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柴荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外甥见驾，舅王千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柴荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "匡胤可曾到来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "柴荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已在午门候旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣他上殿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "柴荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舅王有旨：宣赵匡胤上殿！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天上日月常见面，庶子才得见明君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "草臣，赵匡胤见驾，大王千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何不抬起头来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢仰面视君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恕你无罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤抬头。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（郭威惊。牌子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀斧手，推出斩了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "柴荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！请问舅王，赵匡胤未曾犯罪，为何推出处斩！"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨晚三更时分，偶得一兆，见一红脸大汉将孤左眼伤了一箭，故而欲报梦中之\n仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柴荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梦中之事，不可尽信，还要他扶保江山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇儿保奏，暂赦其罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢千岁不斩之恩！"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是孤不斩于你，皆因柴荣保奏。孤有桩心事，你可愿去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何心事？草臣愿往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你去到燕京刺杀刘化王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柴荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐他多少人马？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！不要人马，草臣一人一骑，七月十三启程，八月十五马到功成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你敢是有逃走之意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣有家眷现在柴府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柴荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！你有什么家眷在我府中啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你何必隐瞒？"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二人不必争论，将赵匡胤家眷押入天牢，候他取了刘王首级，再放出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤、柴荣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请驾回宫！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（郭威、大太监、四太监同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我先前定的是脱身计，\n被他解开肺腑情。\n八月十五把功成！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "柴荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只望接他把王位享，"
        }
